ed="T" n="0749c20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0749c20"/><head><date from-iso="+0947-03-15" key="j20670182068464" to-iso="+0951-02-28">漢</date><placeName key="PL000000023569">洛京法林院</placeName><persName key="A009946">僧照</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0749c21"/><persName key="A009946">釋僧照</persName>，姓張氏，<placeName key="PL000000000368">范陽</placeName>人也。<date key="j20468572047222" from-iso="+0892-01-01" to-iso="+0892-12-31">年十四</date>出家，投<placeName key="PL000000000351">憫<lb
ed="T" n="0749c22"/>忠寺</placeName>，聰晤絕儔，神儀偉秀。初受經偈，日誦<lb
ed="T" n="0749c23"/>數千百言，目所覽者過於宿習<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1256"/>。吐論知見，<lb
ed="T" n="0749c24"/>有老成<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g672"/>之風。遂度為沙彌。受具已來，歷于<lb
ed="T" n="0749c25"/>再閏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1254"/>，暗誦經典，已踰六大部矣，即《最勝王》、<lb
ed="T" n="0749c26"/>《大悲》、《維摩》、《法華》等經。傍加聽尋經、論，十數年<lb
ed="T" n="0749c27"/>間，深文伏義，藍出青<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1257"/>矣。<date notBefore-iso="+0904-09-28" key="j20515102052494" notAfter-iso="+0907-06-09"><name>天祐</name>中</date>，遊方南下，爰<lb
ed="T" n="0749c28"/>屆<placeName key="PL000000002511">中山</placeName>，元戎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1255"/><persName key="A009920">王處直</persName>請住<placeName key="PL000000002495">法華寺</placeName>。相次<ref type="person" target="#A000793">易帥</ref><ptr target="#n1258"/><lb
ed="T" n="0749c29"/>請<ref type="person" target="#A009946">之</ref>，太傅、隴西公連表<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1265"/>薦賜紫方袍，加<persName key="A009946">至<pb ed="T" n="0750a" xml:id="T50.2061.0750a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0750a01"/>真大師</persName>。次則<placeName key="PL000000042848">扶風</placeName><persName key="A009948">馬<roleName>公</roleName></persName>請為僧正，非所好<lb
ed="T" n="0750a02"/>也。及抵<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛陽</placeName>，有命開《法華經》講，止<placeName key="PL000000023569">法林<lb
ed="T" n="0750a03"/>院</placeName>。況乎都闕浩穰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1259"/>，象龍輻湊，及<persName key="A009946">照</persName>之唱導，翕<lb
ed="T" n="0750a04"/>如<ptr type="glossary" target="#g768"/>於下風<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1108"/>伏膺矣。以<date key="j20674422067442" when-iso="+0948-05-12"><name>乾祐</name>元年三月二十六<lb
ed="T" n="0750a05"/>日</date>，示滅于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023569">講院</ref>，春秋七十，僧臘五十。四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/><lb
ed="T" n="0750a06"/>號慕，侍中<persName key="A009955">李<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1260"/>傾<ptr target="#n962"/><placeName key="PL000000002347">易</placeName><placeName key="PL000000002511">定</placeName>，曾為外護，復守<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0750a07"/>宅，飾終喪禮，悉以資奉。粵<date key="j20674492067449" when-iso="+0948-05-19">四月三日</date>遷神于<lb
ed="T" n="0750a08"/>城南，行<anchor xml:id="beg0750001"/>茶<anchor xml:id="end0750001"/>毘法，收舍利，紅潤可數百粒。<lb
ed="T" n="0750a09"/><placeName key="PL000000023476">濟陽</placeName><ptr target="#n1261"/><persName key="A009953">丁<roleName>公</roleName></persName>為保釐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1262"/>之簉職<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1263"/>，為樹塔于<placeName key="PL000000023667">廣化</placeName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0750a10"/>寺南岡。<persName key="A009946">照</persName>平昔講凡七十餘座，勤勤為法。門<lb
ed="T" n="0750a11"/>生頗多。宰臣<persName key="A009927">馬<roleName>公</roleName><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>孫</sic><corr>裔孫</corr></choice></persName><ptr target="#n1264"/>最所欽重，前後贈詩僅<lb
ed="T" n="0750a12"/>數十首，<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛</placeName>中為美談矣。</p>
